#TwoSum Problem on LeetCode
class Solution {
    public int[] twoSum(int[] nums, int target) {
        int n = nums.length;
        for(int i = 0;i<n-1;i++){
            for(int j = i+1;j<n;j++){
                if(nums[i]+nums[j] == target){
                    return new int[]{i,j};
                }
            }
        }
        return new int[]{};
    }
}
#Comment: Took help from the solution section, after that realised the question was really very easy, we need to change our perspective towards approaching a question.
